Package org.eclipse.jst.jsf.contentmodel.annotation.internal.provisional

Interface Summary
ICMAnnotationFileParser Interface used to allow parsing of meta-data files that do not conform to the default schema provided.
ICMAnnotationSourceFileInfo The interface used to access information about the annotationFile extension Not intended to be implemented by clients.
 

Class Summary
CMAnnotationHelper Class meant for all public access to the design-time meta-data (CMAnnotations) values.
CMAnnotationPropertyValue The class used to return result of a query on the annotation model.
CMAnnotationSourceFileLocator Used to supply an InputStream to the parser of an annotation meta-data file and the URL to the resource bundle for a properties file, if any.
